<h1>Hold me, I'm a book.</h1>
<h2>How many holds are on this book at <a href="http://sfpl.org">SFPL?</a></h2>


Enter a title, author, or keyword(s):
<form action="/" method="post">
  <input type="text" name="book">
  <button type = "submit" class = "btn">Search!</button>
</form>
<br>
<% if defined?(@book) %>
  You searched for: "<%= @book %>"
  <% end %>
<br>
<br>
<ul>
<% if defined?(@books) %>
      <% @books.each do |key, value| %>
    <li>
      <a href=<%= @urls[key] %>"><%= key %></a>
      <br>
      <span style="background-color: #44FFB4"><%= value %></span>
    </li>
  <% end %>
<% end %>
</ul>

 <footer><p>The title you've requested may not be in the SFPL system. (It happens!) In that case, check <a href="http://csul.iii.com/">Link+</a>, a "union catalog of contributed holdings from participating libraries in CA and NV," better known
   as a lifeline to rogue researchers near and far.
 </p>
